@startuml
!theme plain
title Epic 26 - US106: Uncle Totò Boss (Sette e Mezzo)

class UncleTotoBoss {
    - loot_item : ItemString = "Ace"
    + start_sette_e_mezzo_challenge()
    + check_game_result(winner)
    + surrender_loot()
}

class SetteEMezzoGame {
    - deck : List<Card>
    - player_score : float
    - boss_score : float
    + deal_initial_card()
    + player_hit() : float
    + player_stand()
    + boss_play_turn()
    + get_final_winner() : Winner
}

class Player {
    + inventory : List<Item>
    + decide_hit_or_stand()
    + receive_item(item)
}

' Relazioni
UncleTotoBoss ..> SetteEMezzoGame : acts as Dealer
SetteEMezzoGame --> Player : interacts with
UncleTotoBoss --> Player : gives Ace on Win

note right of UncleTotoBoss::surrender_loot
  Viene chiamato se il giocatore
  vince contro il Banco (Totò)
end note

@enduml